const checkPrime=e=>{if(e<=2||e%2===0)return false;const r=Math.sqrt(e);for(let i=3;i<=r;i++){if(e%i===0)return false}return true};const isPrime=e=>{if(!Number.isInteger(e))return false;return checkPrime(e)};module.exports={isPrime:isPrime,findPrime:(...e)=>{return e.reduce((e,r)=>{if(Number.isInteger(r)){e.push({number:r,isPrime:checkPrime(r)});return e}return e},[])}};